                <pb facs="1515" n="1491" xml:id="pg_1491"/>
                <p rend="flushleft">I.<hi rend="italic">Date and Meeting Place of the Next Session
                        of the Council of Foreign Ministers</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> that the next session of the Council of
                    Foreign Ministers would commence at Moscow on March 10, 1947.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Proposal by the U.S. Delegation for the
                        Appointment of Special Deputies for the Study of Questions Concerning
                        Germany and Austria</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views, a decision on this question was <hi rend="italic">deferred</hi>.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Agenda for the Next Session of the
                        Council of Foreign Ministers</hi>
                </p>
                <p>(Proposals by the U.S. Delegation [<gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46)
                        (NY)</gloss>57],<note n="63" xml:id="d402fn63">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_1464">p. 1464</ref>. Brackets
                        in this document appear in the source text.</note> the U.S.S.R. Delegation
                        [<gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss>60],<note n="64" xml:id="d402fn64">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, p. 1476.</note> and the French Delegation
                        [<gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss>63].)<note n="65" xml:id="d402fn65">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_1478">p. 1478</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views, it was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to request
                    representatives to draft the text of an agenda for the Council’s next session,
                    and to report back to the Council at its meeting on December 10th.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">IV. <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Tuesday, December 10, 1946, at 11:30 a.m.</p>
